          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 June 16</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:1B</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>From Camp Stephenson, Frederick County, VA. Battle
                  of Winchester.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 July 10</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>From Washington Co., Maryland. Battle of
                  Gettysburg.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 July 19</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>From Camp Near Darksville, Berkeley County, Va.
                  Comments on kindness of people in Pennsylvania and
                  wealth of countryside there.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 July 19</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>From Camp Near Darksville, Berkeley County, Va.
                  Comments on civilians in Pennsylvania and wealth of
                  countryside there.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 August 4</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>From Camp Stonewall Brigade. Difficulty in
                  receiving mail; encamped near Orange Court House</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 August 14</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>From Camp Stonewall Brigade. Still encamped 2 1/2
                  miles from Orange Court House, on the plank road;
                  needs socks, woolen gloves for next winter; also
                  soap.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 mid-August</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>From Camp Stonewall Brigade. Still in camp; no
                  prospect of fighting; he has chance for a furlough
                  next winter.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 August 27</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>From Camp Stonewall Brigade. News of prisoners
                  from Northern paper.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 September 3</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>From Camp Stonewall Brigade. Still in camp doing
                  guard duty; reports news about various other soldiers
                  who were wounded, killed, or taken prisoner.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 September 25</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>Has been on march for ten days and expects battle
                  soon; unit constructing breastworks; news of other
                  soldiers; is tired of fighting but expects war to go
                  on.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 October 6</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>He is on the march twenty miles below Orange Court
                  House; Yankees are tearing up nearby railroads.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 October 21</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>Camp near Culpeper Court House. Reports various
                  engagements against yankees; prisoners taken.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 November 1</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>Drawn up in line of battle.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 November 4</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>In winter camp about seven miles east of the
                  Rappahannock, five miles west of Culpeper
                  Courthouse</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 November 15</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>Camp near Orange Court House; rations low.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 November 21</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>His unit is on the move, rarely stopping more than
                  a few days in one place; a new supply of winter
                  clothes arrived for the brigade, best clothing in
                  some time.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 December 5</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>George Poor wounded; unit still in camp.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1863 December 16</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:2</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>Still in camp; needs socks, red pepper, soap.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1864 January 9</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:3</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>Camp near Orange Court House. In winter quarters,
                  doing guard and picket duty; rations reduced; has no
                  shoes but hopes to get some.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1864 March 8</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:3</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>Camp news; needs socks.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1864 March 24</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:3</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>Deep snow; units have snowfights.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1864 April 5</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:3</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>Weather bad and rations very poor; he has obtained
                  a Catholic prayer book.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Letter, 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1864 April 22</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
                  1:3</container>
          </did>
